OL,3,CPassengers allowed to leave norovirus-
OL,4,Chit cruise ship in France
OL,6,FA norovirus-hit cruise ship carrying
OL,7,FBritish and Irish passengers has had
OL,8,Fits lockdown order lifted.
OL,10,FAll 1,701 people on board the Ambition
OL,11,Fwere stopped from disembarking for
OL,12,Fmore than 24 hours after the ship
OL,13,Fdocked in Bordeaux on Tuesday,
OL,14,Ffollowing the death of one person and
OL,15,Fdozens of cases of norovirus.
OL,17,FLocal authorities allowed those
OL,18,Fwithout symptoms to disembark from
OL,19,FWednesday afternoon, while those who
OL,20,Fhad been infected were ordered to
OL,21,Fremain on board in isolation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
