OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778832412
OL,3,CPassengers allowed to leave norovirus-
OL,4,Chit cruise ship in France
OL,6,FThe person who died was a 92-year-old
OL,7,FBritish man who had a heart attack.
OL,9,FHis death appears to be unrelated to
OL,10,Fthe norovirus outbreak, health
OL,11,Fauthorities said.
OL,13,FEssex-based operator Ambassador Cruise
OL,14,FLine said on Wednesday that 48
OL,15,Fpassengers and one crew member had
OL,16,F"active cases of gastrointestinal
OL,17,Fillness".
OL,19,FThere were a total of 1,187 passengers
OL,20,Fand 514 crew members onboard.
