OL,3,CPassengers allowed to leave norovirus-
OL,4,Chit cruise ship in France
OL,6,FNorovirus is a highly contagious form
OL,7,Fof gastroenteritis that causes
OL,8,Fvomiting and diarrhoea.
OL,10,FThe ship set sail from Belfast on May
OL,11,F8 and called at Liverpool a day later,
OL,12,Ffor a 14-night voyage to France and
OL,13,FSpain.
OL,15,FCases of gastroenteritis increased
OL,16,Fafter the embarkation of passengers in
OL,17,FLiverpool.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
