OL,3,CPassengers allowed to leave norovirus-
OL,4,Chit cruise ship in France
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAmbassador Cruise Line said in a
OL,12,Fstatement: "We would like to reassure
OL,13,Fguests that we take any illnesses
OL,14,Faboard our fleet extremely seriously.
OL,16,F"Enhanced sanitation and prevention
OL,17,Fprotocols were immediately implemented
OL,18,Facross the ship in line with
OL,19,Festablished public health procedures
OL,20,Ffollowing the initial reports of
OL,21,Fillness.
