PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1778832412
OL,3,CPassengers allowed to leave norovirus-
OL,4,Chit cruise ship in France
OL,6,F"The comprehensive health and safety
OL,7,Fmeasures introduced include increased
OL,8,Fcleaning and disinfection measures in
OL,9,Fpublic areas, assisted service in
OL,10,Fselected dining venues and ongoing
OL,11,Fguidance to guests regarding hand
OL,12,Fhygiene, including regular hand
OL,13,Fwashing, use of hand sanitisers and
OL,14,Fthe prompt reporting of any symptoms
OL,15,Fto the onboard medical team."
OL,17,FA spokesman for the cruise line said
OL,18,Fthere was no link with the outbreak of
OL,19,Fhantavirus on the MV Hondius cruise
OL,20,Fship.
